      "content": "yo im running a noir detective game for my friends and i need help with a scene. the crime happened in this really rough part of the city, like one of those old urban areas with high-rise public housing, lots of graffiti, and basically no security or street lights. its the kind of place where people just keep their heads down to stay out of trouble. a local shopkeeper got robbed at gunpoint in front of his store. based on the vibe of that neighborhood and the crime, what kind of suspect profile should my detective be looking for to keep the story realistic?",
